    "user_title": "Manage Nx Monorepos with AI Guidance",
    "value_statement": "Large Nx workspaces make dependency analysis, affected builds, and code generation hard to coordinate. This skill gives Claude, Codex, and Claude Code practical guidance for common Nx monorepo workflows.",
    "seo_keywords": [
      "Claude",
      "Codex",
      "Claude Code",
      "Nx monorepo",
      "Nx CLI",
      "project graph",
      "affected builds",
